i studia jsou schopni realizovat vlastn\\u00ed um\\u011bleck\\u00e9 z\\u00e1m\\u011bry: studovat podklady a na jejich z\\u00e1klad\\u011b vypracovat v\\u00fdtvarn\\u00fd n\\u00e1vrh i s technickou dokumentac\\u00ed, spr\\u00e1vn\\u011b zvolit materi\\u00e1l a pracovn\\u00ed postup pro zhotoven\\u00ed v\\u00fdrobku, vytv\\u00e1\\u0159et um\\u011bleck\\u00e9 v\\u00fdrobky v oblasti pap\\u00edrov\\u00e9, textiln\\u00ed nebo d\\u0159ev\\u011bn\\u00e9 hra\\u010dky.</p>\\n\\n<p>Na\\u0161i absolventi jsou d\\u00edky tomu kvalitn\\u011b p\\u0159ipraveni jak pro p\\u0159\\u00edpadn\\u00e9 dal\\u0161\\u00ed studium na vysok\\u00fdch \\u0161kol\\u00e1ch um\\u011bleck\\u00e9ho zam\\u011b\\u0159en\\u00ed, tak i pro vlastn\\u00ed um\\u011bleckou tvorbu spojenou s\\u00a0kouzeln\\u00fdm d\\u011btsk\\u00fdm sv\\u011btem.</p>\\n\"}, \"model\": \"djangocms_text_ckeditor.text\", \"pk\": 931}]','Design hraček 82-41-M/08...',22,629),(19277,'932',932,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"changed_date\": \"2016-10-06T21:30:17Z\", \"language\": \"cs\", \"parent\": null, \"numchild\": 0, \"creation_date\": \"2016-10-06T14:26:38Z\", \"depth\": 1, \"position\": 0, \"path\": \"0045\", \"placeholder\": 96, \"plugin_type\": \"TextPlugin\"}, \"model\": \"cms.cmsplugin\", \"pk\": 932}]','932',15,629),(19278,'92',92,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"slot\": \"content\", \"default_width\": null}, \"model\": \"cms.placeholder\", \"pk\": 92}]','content',1,629),(19279,'93',93,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"slot\": \"sidebar\", \"default_width\": null}, \"model\": \"cms.placeholder\", \"pk\": 93}]','sidebar',1,629),(19280,'94',94,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"slot\": \"feature\", \"default_width\": null}, \"model\": \"cms.placeholder\", \"pk\": 94}]','feature',1,629),(19281,'95',95,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"slot\": \"obor\", \"default_width\": null}, \"model\": \"cms.placeholder\", \"pk\": 95}]','obor',1,629),(19282,'96',96,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"slot\": \"logo\", \"default_width\": null}, \"model\": \"cms.placeholder\", \"pk\": 96}]',