),(19724,'2588',2588,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"body\": \"<h1>Grafick\\u00fd design</h1>\\n\\n<h4><strong>82-41-M/05 (po\\u010det p\\u0159ij\\u00edman\\u00fdch \\u017e\\u00e1k\\u016f 12)</strong></h4>\\n\\n<p>Sou\\u010d\\u00e1st\\u00ed studia oboru je jak u\\u017eit\\u00e1 grafika (grafick\\u00fd design), tak voln\\u00e1 grafick\\u00e1 tvorba vyu\\u017e\\u00edvaj\\u00edc\\u00ed rozmanit\\u00fdch v\\u00fdtvarn\\u00fdch technik.</p>\\n\\n<p>\\u017d\\u00e1ci jsou vedeni k\\u00a0tomu, aby znakem, symbolem i p\\u00edsmem dok\\u00e1zali vyj\\u00e1d\\u0159it svou my\\u0161lenku, osobit\\u00fd pohled na sv\\u011bt. Vlastn\\u00ed n\\u00e1vrhy i jejich praktickou realizaci konzultuj\\u00ed se sv\\u00fdmi u\\u010diteli, jejich\\u017e hlavn\\u00ed snahou je rozv\\u00edjet talent sv\\u00fdch \\u017e\\u00e1k\\u016f a z\\u00e1rove\\u0148 je nau\\u010dit v\\u0161em pot\\u0159ebn\\u00fdm dovednostem um\\u011bleck\\u00e9ho \\u0159emesla. Ty z\\u00edsk\\u00e1vaj\\u00ed budouc\\u00ed v\\u00fdtvarn\\u00edci v\\u00a0odborn\\u00fdch p\\u0159edm\\u011btech: p\\u00edsmo, fotografie, v\\u00fdtvarn\\u00e1 p\\u0159\\u00edprava, grafick\\u00e9 techniky\\u2026 V pr\\u016fb\\u011bhu studia se rovn\\u011b\\u017e sezn\\u00e1m\\u00ed se specifikou tvorby plak\\u00e1tu, obalov\\u00e9 grafiky, ilustrace, grafickou \\u00fapravou knih, zpracov\\u00e1n\\u00edm firemn\\u00edho loga i kompletn\\u00edch propaga\\u010dn\\u00edch materi\\u00e1l\\u016f. Vedle tradi\\u010dn\\u00edch grafick\\u00fdch prost\\u0159edk\\u016f se pro svou pr\\u00e1ci nau\\u010d\\u00ed pou\\u017e\\u00edvat modern\\u00ed po\\u010d\\u00edta\\u010dovou techniku, bez nich\\u017e se sou\\u010dasn\\u00fd grafik u\\u017e neobejde.</p>\\n\\n<p>A kde absolventi tohoto bou\\u0159liv\\u011b se vyv\\u00edjej\\u00edc\\u00edho oboru nach\\u00e1zej\\u00ed uplatn\\u011bn\\u00ed? Zejm\\u00e9na v\\u00a0reklamn\\u00edm a marketingov\\u00e9m pr\\u016fmyslu jako samostatn\\u00ed v\\u00fdtvarn\\u00edci, ale i\\u00a0 jako zam\\u011bstnanci reklamn\\u00edch studi\\u00ed nebo agentur.</p>\\n\\n<p>\\u00a0</p>\\n\"}, \"model\": \"djangocms_text_ckeditor.text\", \"pk\": 2588}]','Grafický design 82-41-M/05...',22,649),(19725,'2586',2586,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"changed_date\": \"2016-10-09T17:41:14Z\", \"language\": \"cs\", \"parent\": null, \"numchild\": 1, \"creation_date\": \"2016-10-09T17:35:44Z\", \"depth\": 1, \"position\": 0, \"path\": \"00A1\", \"placeholder\": 227, \"plugin_type\": \"StylePlugin\"}, \"model\": \"cms.cmsplugin\", \"pk\": 2586}]','2586',15,649),(19726,'2587',2587,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"changed_date\": \"2016-10-09T17:36:19Z\", \"language\": \"cs\", \"parent\": null, \"numchild\": 0, \"creation_date\": \"2016-10-09T17:36:10Z\", \"depth\": 1, \"position\": 0, \"path\": \"00A2\", \"placeholder\": 230, \"plugin_type\": \"TextPlugin\"}, \"model\": \"cms.cmsplugin\", \"pk\": 2587}]','2587',15,649),(19727,'37',37,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"menu_title\": \"Grafick\\u00fd design\", \"meta_description\": \"Grafick\\u00fd design\", \"page_title\": \"Grafick\\u00fd design\", \"language\": \"cs\", \"title\": \"Grafick\\u00fd design\", \"has_url_overwrite\": true, \"redirect\": \"\", \"page\": 40, \"published\": true, \"path\": \"grafika\", \"creation_date\": \"2016-10-09T17:34:37Z\", \"slug\": \"grafika\"}, \"model\": \"cms.title\", \"pk\": 37}]','Grafický design (grafika, cs)',16,649),(19728,'227',227,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"slot\": \"content\", \"default_width\": null}, \"model\": \"cms.placeholder\", \"pk\": 227}]','content',1,649),(19729,'40',40,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"navigation_extenders\": \"\", \"site\": 1, \"application_namespace\": null, \"path\": \"000A0005\", \"in_navigation\": true, \"reverse_id\": null, \"login_required\": false, \"created_by\": \"admin\", \"languages\": \"cs\", \"publication_end_date\": null, \"template\": \"obory.html\", \"placeholders\": [227, 228, 229, 230, 231], \"changed_date\": \"2016-10-09T17:42:16Z\", \"limit_visibility_in_menu\": null, \"parent\": 7, \"numchild\": 0, \"so