d\\u00ed pou\\u017e\\u00edvat modern\\u00ed po\\u010d\\u00edta\\u010dovou techniku, bez nich\\u017e se sou\\u010dasn\\u00fd grafik u\\u017e neobejde.</p>\\n\\n<p>A kde absolventi tohoto bou\\u0159liv\\u011b se vyv\\u00edjej\\u00edc\\u00edho oboru nach\\u00e1zej\\u00ed uplatn\\u011bn\\u00ed? Zejm\\u00e9na v\\u00a0reklamn\\u00edm a marketingov\\u00e9m pr\\u016fmyslu jako samostatn\\u00ed v\\u00fdtvarn\\u00edci, ale i\\u00a0 jako zam\\u011bstnanci reklamn\\u00edch studi\\u00ed nebo agentur.</p>\\n\\n<p>\\u00a0</p>\\n\"}, \"model\": \"djangocms_text_ckeditor.text\", \"pk\": 2588}]','Grafický design 82-41-M/05...',22,650),(19769,'2586',2586,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"changed_date\": \"2016-10-09T17:41:14Z\", \"language\": \"cs\", \"parent\": null, \"numchild\": 1, \"creation_date\": \"2016-10-09T17:35:44Z\", \"depth\": 1, \"position\": 0, \"path\": \"00A1\", \"placeholder\": 227, \"plugin_type\": \"StylePlugin\"}, \"model\": \"cms.cmsplugin\", \"pk\": 2586}]','2586',15,650),(19770,'2587',2587,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"changed_date\": \"2016-10-09T17:36:19Z\", \"language\": \"cs\", \"parent\": null, \"numchild\": 0, \"creation_date\": \"2016-10-09T17:36:10Z\", \"depth\": 1, \"position\": 0, \"path\": \"00A2\", \"placeholder\": 230, \"plugin_type\": \"TextPlugin\"}, \"model\": \"cms.cmsplugin\", \"pk\": 2587}]','2587',15,650),(19771,'37',37,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"menu_title\": \"Grafick\\u00fd design\", \"meta_description\": \"Grafick\\u00fd design\", \"page_title\": \"Grafick\\u00fd design\", \"language\": \"cs\", \"title\": \"Grafick\\u00fd design\", \"has_url_overwrite\": true, \"redirect\": \"\", \"page\": 40, \"published\": true, \"path\": \"grafika\", \"creation_date\": \"2016-10-09T17:34:37Z\", \"slug\": \"grafika\"}, \"model\": \"cms.title\", \"pk\": 37}]','Grafický design (grafika, cs)',16,650),(19772,'227',227,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"slot\": \"content\", \"default_width\": null}, \"model\": \"cms.placeholder\", \"pk\": 227}]','content',1,650),(19773,'40',40,'json