fdch technik.</p>\\n\\n<p>\\u017d\\u00e1ci jsou vedeni k\\u00a0tomu, aby znakem, symbolem i p\\u00edsmem dok\\u00e1zali vyj\\u00e1d\\u0159it svou my\\u0161lenku, osobit\\u00fd pohled na sv\\u011bt. Vlastn\\u00ed n\\u00e1vrhy i jejich praktickou realizaci konzultuj\\u00ed se sv\\u00fdmi u\\u010diteli, jejich\\u017e hlavn\\u00ed snahou je rozv\\u00edjet talent sv\\u00fdch \\u017e\\u00e1k\\u016f a z\\u00e1rove\\u0148 je nau\\u010dit v\\u0161em pot\\u0159ebn\\u00fdm dovednostem um\\u011bleck\\u00e9ho \\u0159emesla. Ty z\\u00edsk\\u00e1vaj\\u00ed budouc\\u00ed v\\u00fdtvarn\\u00edci v\\u00a0odborn\\u00fdch p\\u0159edm\\u011btech: p\\u00edsmo, fotografie, v\\u00fdtvarn\\u00e1 p\\u0159\\u00edprava, grafick\\u00e9 techniky\\u2026 V pr\\u016fb\\u011bhu studia se rovn\\u011b\\u017e sezn\\u00e1m\\u00ed se specifikou tvorby plak\\u00e1tu, obalov\\u00e9 grafiky, ilustrace, grafickou \\u00fapravou knih, zpracov\\u00e1n\\u00edm firemn\\u00edho loga i kompletn\\u00edch propaga\\u010dn\\u00edch materi\\u00e1l\\u016f. Vedle tradi\\u010dn\\u00edch grafick\\u00fdch prost\\u0159edk\\u016f se pro svou pr\\u00e1ci nau\\u010d\\u00ed pou\\u017e\\u00edvat modern\\u00ed po\\u010d\\u00edta\\u010dovou techniku, bez nich\\u017e se sou\\u010dasn\\u00fd grafik u\\u017e neobejde.</p>\\n\\n<p>A kde absolventi tohoto bou\\u0159liv\\u011b se vyv\\u00edjej\\u00edc\\u00edho oboru nach\\u00e1zej\\u00ed uplatn\\u011bn\\u00ed? Zejm\\u00e9na v\\u00a0reklamn\\u00edm a marketingov\\u00e9m pr\\u016fmyslu jako samostatn\\u00ed v\\u00fdtvarn\\u00edci, ale i\\u00a0 jako zam\\u011bstnanci reklamn\\u00edch studi\\u00ed nebo agentur.</p>\\n\\n<p>\\u00a0</p>\\n\"}, \"model\": \"djangocms_text_ckeditor.text\", \"pk\": 2588}]','Grafický design 82-41-M/05...',22,654),(19943,'2586',2586,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"changed_date\": \"2016-10-09T17:41:14Z\", \"language\": \"cs\", \"parent\": null, \"numchild\": 1, \"creation_date\": \"2016-10-09T17:35:44Z\", \"depth\": 1, \"position\": 0, \"path\": \"00A1\", \"placeholder\": 2