/h2>\\n\\n<h3>Odborn\\u00e9 znalosti a dovednosti</h3>\\n\\n<p class=\\\"western\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.28cm; line-height: 107%\\\">Vzd\\u011bl\\u00e1v\\u00e1n\\u00ed je sm\\u011brov\\u00e1no k tomu, aby absolvent:</p>\\n\\n<ul>\\n\\t<li class=\\\"western\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.28cm; line-height: 107%;\\\">navrhoval a konstruoval strojn\\u00ed sou\\u010d\\u00e1sti, mechanismy a jejich \\u010d\\u00e1sti, n\\u00e1stroje, n\\u00e1\\u0159ad\\u00ed, p\\u0159\\u00edpravky a dal\\u0161\\u00ed v\\u00fdrobn\\u00ed pom\\u016fcky;</li>\\n\\t<li class=\\\"western\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.28cm; line-height: 107%;\\\">projektoval technick\\u00e9 vybaven\\u00ed budov a technologick\\u00e9 vybaven\\u00ed pracovi\\u0161\\u0165;</li>\\n\\t<li class=\\\"western\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.28cm; line-height: 107%;\\\">pou\\u017e\\u00edval aplika\\u010dn\\u00ed programy pro po\\u010d\\u00edta\\u010dovou podporu projektov\\u00e9 dokumentace a konstruk\\u010dn\\u00ed p\\u0159\\u00edpravu v\\u00fdroby jako n\\u00e1stroje pro ztv\\u00e1rn\\u011bn\\u00ed sv\\u00fdch my\\u0161lenek a n\\u00e1pad\\u016f a jako prost\\u0159edek pro jejich realizaci;</li>\\n\\t<li class=\\\"western\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.28cm; line-height: 107%;\\\">navrhoval zp\\u016fsoby, technick\\u00e1 za\\u0159\\u00edzen\\u00ed, n\\u00e1stroje, v\\u00fdrobn\\u00ed pom\\u016fcky a technologick\\u00e9 podm\\u00ednky k p\\u0159etvo\\u0159en\\u00ed surovin, p\\u0159edv\\u00fdrobk\\u016f a polotovar\\u016f ve v\\u00fdrobek;</li>\\n\\t<li class=\\\"western\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.28cm; line-height: 107%;\\\">navrhoval technologick\\u00e9 postupy v\\u00fdroby a mont\\u00e1\\u017en\\u00ed postupy podskupin a skupin v\\u00fdrobk\\u016f a zp\\u016fsoby a podm\\u00ednky kontroly jejich jakosti;</li>\\n\\t<li class=\\\"western\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.28cm; line-height: 107%;\\\">vytv\\u00e1\\u0159el a pou\\u017e\\u00edval programy pro vykon\\u00e1v\\u00e1n\\u00ed pracovn\\u00edch operac\\u00ed na \\u010d\\u00edslicov\\u011b \\u0159\\u00edzen\\u00fdch stroj\\u00edch prost\\u0159ednictv\\u00edm aplika\\u010dn\\u00edch program\\u016f pro po\\u010d\\u00edta\\u010dovou podporu technologick\\u00e9 p\\u0159\\u00edpravy v\\u00fdroby pou\\u017e\\u00edvan\\u00fdch jako n\\u00e1stroje pro ztv\\u00e1rn\\u011bn\\u00ed sv\\u00fdch my\\u0161lenek a n\\u00e1pad\\u016f a jako prost\\u0159edek pro jejich realizaci;</li>\\n\\t<li>\\n\\t<p class=\\\"western\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.28cm; line-height: 107%\\\">navrhoval syst\\u00e9m p\\u00e9\\u010de o technick\\u00fd stav stroj\\u016f a za\\u0159\\u00edzen\\u00ed, zp\\u016fsoby diagnostiky jejich technick\\u00e9ho stavu, postupy pr\\u00e1ce p\\u0159i jejich reviz\\u00edch, \\u00fadr\\u017eb\\u011b a oprav\\u00e1ch; objedn\\u00e1val pot\\u0159ebn\\u00e9 n\\u00e1hradn\\u00ed d\\u00edly a komponenty pro stroje a za\\u0159\\u00edzen\\u00ed a zpracov\\u00e1val n\\u00e1vrhy inovac\\u00ed stroj\\u016f a strojn\\u00edch za\\u0159\\u00edzen\\u00ed;</p>\\n\\t</li>\\n\\t<li>\\n\\t<p class=\\\"western\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.28cm; line-height: 107%\\\">m\\u011b\\u0159il technick\\u00e9 veli\\u010diny za pou\\u017eit\\u00ed m\\u011b\\u0159idel a m\\u011b\\u0159\\u00edc\\u00edch p\\u0159\\u00edstroj\\u016f a vhodn\\u011b aplikoval b\\u011b\\u017en\\u00e9 zp\\u016fsoby kontroly a m\\u011b\\u0159en\\u00ed technick\\u00fdch veli\\u010din;</p>\\n\\t</li>\\n\\t<li>\\n\\t<p class=\\\"western\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.28cm; line-height: 107%\\\">analyzoval a vyhodnocoval v\\u00fdsledky proveden\\u00fdch m\\u011b\\u0159en\\u00ed a zpracov\\u00e1val o nich z\\u00e1znamy a protokoly.</p>\\n\\t</li>\\n</ul>\\n\"}, \"model\": \"djangocms_text_ckeditor.text\", \"pk\": 2624}]','Profil studenta Odborné...',22,656),(20023,'2586',2586,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"margin_right\": null, \"class_name\": \"\", \"padding_bottom\": null, \"additional_class_names\": \"obor-uvod\", \"label\": \"\", \"id_name\": \"\", \"padding_right\": null, \"margin_top\": null, \"padding_left\": null, \"padding_top\": null, \"margin_bottom\": null, \"margin_left\": null, \"tag_type\": \"div\"}, \"model\": \"aldryn_style.style\", \"pk\": 2586}]','div (obor-uvod)',55,656),(20024,'2587',2587,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"changed_date\": \"2016-10-09T17:36:19Z\", \"language\": \"cs\", \"parent\": null, \"numchild\": 0, \"creation_date\": \"2016-10-09T17:36:10Z\", \"depth\": 1, \"position\": 0, \"path\": \"00A2\", \"placeholder\": 230, \"plugin_type\": \"TextPlugin\"}, \"model\": \"cms.cmsplugin\", \"pk\": 2587}]','2587',15,656),(20025,'2588',2588,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"body\": \"<h1>Grafick\\u00fd design</h1>\\n\\n<h4><strong>82-41-M/05 (po\\u010det p\\u0159ij\\u00edman\\u00fdch \\u017e\\u00e1k\\u016f 12)</strong></h4>\\n\\n<p>Sou\\u010d\\u00e1st\\u00ed studia oboru je jak u\\u017eit\\u00e1 grafika (grafick\\u00fd design), tak voln\\u00e1 grafick\\u00e1 tvorba vyu\\u017e\\u00edvaj\\u00edc\\u00ed rozmanit\\u00fdch v\\u00fdtvarn\\u00fdch technik.</p>\\n\\n<p>\\u017d\\u00e1ci jsou vedeni k\\u00a0tomu, aby znakem, symbolem i p\\u00edsmem dok\\u00e1zali vyj\\u00e1d\\u0159it svou my\\u0161lenku, osobit\\u00fd pohled na sv\\u011bt. Vlastn\\u00ed n\\u00e1vrhy i jejich praktickou realizaci konzultuj\\u00ed se sv\\u00fdmi u\\u010diteli, jejich\\u017e hlavn\\u00ed snahou je rozv\\u00edjet talent sv\\u00fdch \\u017e\\u00e1k\\u016f a z\\u00e1rove\\u0148 je nau\\u010dit v\\u0161em pot\\u0159ebn\\u00fdm dovednostem um\\u011bleck\\u00e9ho \\u0159emesla. Ty z\\u00edsk\\u00e1vaj\\u00ed budouc\\u00ed v\\u00fdtvarn\\u00edci v\\u00a0odborn\\u00fdch p\\u0159edm\\u011btech: p\\u00edsmo, fotografie, v\\u00fdtvarn\\u00e1 p\\u0159\\u00edprava, grafick\\u00e9 techniky\\u2026 V pr\\u016fb\\u011bhu studia se rovn\\u011b\\u017e sezn\\u00e1m\\u00ed se specifikou tvorby plak\\u00e1tu, obalov\\u00e9 grafiky, ilustrace, grafickou \\u00fapravou knih, zpracov\\u00e1n\\u00edm firemn\\u00edho loga i kompletn\\u00edch propaga\\u010dn\\u00edch materi\\u00e1l\\u016f. Vedle tradi\\u010dn\\u00edch grafick\\u00fdch prost\\u0159edk\\u016f se pro svou pr\\u00e1ci nau\\u010d\\u00ed pou\\u017e\\u00edvat modern\\u00ed po\\u010d\\u00edta\\u010dovou techniku, bez nich\\u017e se sou\\u010dasn\\u00fd grafik u\\u017e neobejde.</p>\\n\\n<p>A kde absolventi tohoto bou\\u0159liv\\u011b se vyv\\u00edjej\\u00edc\\u00edho oboru nach\\u00e1zej\\u00ed uplatn\\u011bn\\u00ed? Zejm\\u00e9na v\\u00a0reklamn\\u00edm a marketingov\\u00e9m pr\\u016fmyslu jako samostatn\\u00ed v\\u00fdtvarn\\u00edci, ale i\\u00a0 jako zam\\u011bstnanci reklamn\\u00edch studi\\u00ed nebo agentur.</p>\\n\\n<p>\\u00a0</p>\\n\"}, \"model\": \"djangocms_text_ckeditor.text\", \"pk\": 2588}]','Grafický design 82-41-M/05...',22,656),(20026,'2586',2586,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"changed_date\": \"2016-10-09T17:41:14Z\", \"language\": \"cs\", \"parent\": null, \"numchild\": 1, \"creation_date\": \"2016-10-09T17:35:44Z\", \"depth\": 1, \"position\": 0, \"path\": \"00A1\", \"placeholder\": 227, \"plugin_type\": \"StylePlugin\"}, \"model\": \"cms.cmsplugin\", \"pk\": 2586}]','2586',15,656),(20027,'2587',2587,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"body\": \"grafika\"}, \"model\": \"djangocms_text_ckeditor.text\", \"pk\": 2587}]','grafika',22,656),(20028,'37',37,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"menu_title\": \"Grafick\\u00fd design\", \"meta_description\": \"Grafick\\u00fd design\", \"page_title\": \"Grafick\\u00fd design\", \"language\": \"cs\", \"title\": \"Grafick\\u00fd design\", \"has_url_overwrite\": true, \"redirect\": \"\", \"page\": 40, \"published\": true, \"path\": \"grafika\", \"creation_date\": \"2016-10-09T17:34:37Z\", \"slug\": \"grafika\"}, \"model\": \"cms.title\", \"pk\": 37}]','Grafický design (grafika, cs)',16,656),(20029,'40',40,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"navigation_extenders\": \"\", \"site\": 1, \"application_namespace\": null, \"path\": \"000A0005\", \"in_navigation\": true, \"reverse_id\": null, \"login_required\": false, \"created_by\": \"admin\", \"languages\": \"cs\", \"publication_end_