00e9 projekty ji\\u017e b\\u011bhem sv\\u00e9 odborn\\u00e9 praxe.</p>\\n\\n<p>\\u0160kola disponuje pot\\u0159ebn\\u00fdm technick\\u00fdm vybaven\\u00edm (3D tisk\\u00e1rna, CNC obr\\u00e1b\\u011bc\\u00ed stroje \\u2026) i software (CAD/CAM) pro plnohodnotnou v\\u00fduku v\\u0161ech odborn\\u00fdch p\\u0159edm\\u011bt\\u016f.</p>\\n\\n<p>V\\u00fduka konstruov\\u00e1n\\u00ed na po\\u010d\\u00edta\\u010di prob\\u00edh\\u00e1 v programech AutoCAD a Autodesk Inventor; studenti d\\u00edky tomu mohou z\\u00edskat ofici\\u00e1ln\\u00ed certifik\\u00e1t od firmy Autodesk.</p>\\n\\n<p><img id=\\\"plugin_obj_2409\\\" title=\\\"Link/Button - \\u0160koln\\u00ed vzd\\u011bl\\u00e1vac\\u00ed pl\\u00e1n oboru stroj\\u00edrenstv\\u00ed\\\" alt=\\\"Link/Button\\\" src=\\\"/static/aldryn_bootstrap3/img/type/button.png\\\"></p>\\n\"}, \"model\": \"djangocms_text_ckeditor.text\", \"pk\": 140}]','Strojírenství 23-41-M/01 Strojírenství...',22,674),(20423,'173',173,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"body\": \"<p><a href=\\\"/\\\" class=\\\"navbar-brand\\\"><img class=\\\"img img-responsive\\\" alt=\\\"S\\u0160PU Opava\\\" src=\\\"/static/img/logo-skoly-inverse.png\\\"></a></p>\\n\"}, \"model\": \"djangocms_text_ckeditor.text\", \"pk\": 173}]','',22,674),(20424,'2192',2192,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"md_push\": null, \"md_pull\": null, \"lg_col\": 12, \"xs_offset\": null, \"lg_push\": null, \"xs_push\": null, \"sm_offset\": null, \"tag\": \"div\", \"md_col\": null, \"lg_offset\": null, \"classes\": \"nopadding frontpage-actual\", \"sm_push\": null, \"md_offset\": null, \"xs_col\": null, \"sm_pull\": null, \"sm_col\": null, \"lg_pull\": null, \"xs_pull\": null}, \"model\": \"aldryn_bootstrap3.bootstrap3columnplugin\", \"pk\": 2192}]','col-lg-12 nopadding frontpage-actual',80,674),(20425,'1522',1522,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"theme\": \"compact\", \"options\": \"\"}, \"model\": \"djangocms_unitegallery.gallery\", \"pk\": 1522}]','Compact',89,674),(20426,'2194',2194,'json','[{\"fields\": {\"body\": \"<h2>